commit.message: Fix electric index, emissions do not depend on speed
When the mouse passes over a segment, a text displays the CO2 emissions of that segment
Add warnings for unsupported vehicles in transit routes
Add new field to the emissions camp to classify different kind of emissions, only co2 is calculated
Add Makefile and emissions on all levels of the route tree
Output of the application is the same json file as input with the emissions appended on each step
